@startuml
title /exit Sequence

actor User
participant Ui
participant CG2StocksTracker
participant Parser

User -> Ui : /exit
Ui -> CG2StocksTracker : command text
CG2StocksTracker -> Parser : parse(...)
Parser --> CG2StocksTracker : EXIT
CG2StocksTracker -> Ui : showGoodbye()
CG2StocksTracker --> Ui : stop main loop
@enduml
